DevOps Perspective :::::::::::::-
	
	====> Roles & Responsibilies of DevOps Team :			
			
			Jenkins Administration 
				1- Installation of Jenkins
				2- Global System Configurations 
				3- Plugins Management 
				4- Tools Management 
				5- User Management 	------				# To enable User Authentication
				6- Security Management	------			# To enable User Authorization
				7- Credential Management 
				8- Master/Slave Node Configurations
				9- Creation CICD Pipeline Projects 
				10- Onboard Applications to use Jenkins CICD Projects  
				11- Periodic Upgrade of Jenkins and its plugins 
				12- Periodic Backup 
				13- Troubleshooting the Issues!	
	
